Nollywood actor, Yul Edochie, has responded to critics’ insults in regards to his second marriage to the Nigerian actress, Nigerian actress, Judy Austin. Recall that the actor on Wednesday via his Instagram page announced the existence of his son and his marriage to the mother of the child, declaring her publicly as his second wife. According to the actor in his latest Instagram post on Thursday, he is a real man for owning up and taking responsibility for his child from his second wife. Edochie wrote, “Real men own up and take responsibility.Fake men dey hide for back dey run am. “EZEDIKE! Na man you be.”